name: MaintenancePlan

fields.inlineHelpText: Set the work type that governs the duration, required skills and products, and linked articles inherited by generated work orders.
fields.label: Work Type ID
fields.name: WorkTypeId

fields.inlineHelpText: The suggested date of service for the work order in the next batch generated. The value is updated after each batch is generated.
fields.label: Date of the first work order in the next batch
fields.name: NextSuggestedMaintenanceDate

fields.inlineHelpText: The number of days before the work order’s suggested service date in which the service appointment can be scheduled.
fields.label: Maintenance Window Start (Days)
fields.name: MaintenanceWindowStartDays

fields.inlineHelpText: The number of days after the work order’s suggested service date in which the service appointment can be scheduled.
fields.label: Maintenance Window End (Days)
fields.name: MaintenanceWindowEndDays

fields.inlineHelpText: The unit of frequency for the generation timeframe.
fields.label: Generation Timeframe Type
fields.name: GenerationTimeframeType

fields.inlineHelpText: The time in advance that work orders are generated in each batch. The unit is specified in Generation Timeframe Type.
fields.label: Generation Timeframe
fields.name: GenerationTimeframe

fields.inlineHelpText: Set the number of days before the Date of the first work order in the next batch on which work order batches are generated.
fields.label: Generation Horizon (Days)
fields.name: GenerationHorizon

fields.inlineHelpText: Specify whether to generate the new batch on completion of the last work order in the previous batch.
fields.label: Generate new batch upon completion
fields.name: DoesGenerateUponCompletion

fields.inlineHelpText: Define whether work orders are generated automatically. This rule disables the ability to manually generate work orders.
fields.label: Auto-generate work orders
fields.name: DoesAutoGenerateWorkOrders

fields.inlineHelpText: Specify how work orders are generated when more than one asset is associated with the maintenance plan.
fields.label: Work Order Generation Method
fields.name: WorkOrderGenerationMethod

picklistValues.label: One work order line item per asset

fields.inlineHelpText: Specify how service appointments are generated when more than one asset is associated with the maintenance plan and work order generation method is One work order line item per asset.
fields.label: Service Appointment Generation Method
fields.name: SvcApptGenerationMethod

picklistValues.label: One service appointment per work order
One service appointment per work order line item

query: SELECT  CurrencyIsoCode, WorkTypeId, AccountId, ServiceContractId, StartDate, EndDate, NextSuggestedMaintenanceDate, MaintenanceWindowStartDays, MaintenanceWindowEndDays, GenerationTimeframeType, GenerationTimeframe, Description, LocationId, ContactId, MaintenancePlanTitle, GenerationHorizon, DoesGenerateUponCompletion, DoesAutoGenerateWorkOrders, WorkOrderGenerationMethod, SvcApptGenerationMethod FROM MaintenancePlan
